(27, 'mojo_region_2', 'Mojo Region 2', 'index', '\n<div>\n	Cash flow is often a key barrier to business growth. Our services&nbsp;embrace this fact and in recent years we have developed&nbsp;ground-breaking financial models to drive down liabilities to&nbsp;enable strategic development across marketing and other&nbsp;business principles for growth. This essentially involves us&nbsp;creating more cash into the clients business to&nbsp;enable them to exist, evolve and prosper.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n', 2),
(28, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'index', '\n<p class="font_15">\n	Brand&amp;Business exists to drive client performance&nbsp;and profitability. We are unique in that we blend the&nbsp;typically distant worlds of finance, marketing and&nbsp;business services to create highly optimised&nbsp;outcomes for our clients.</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 2),
(29, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'about', '<p class="font_12">Brand&amp;Business was founded by UK SME marketer Stuart Dawson and the four founding partners of<br />\n            Epoch Wealth Management; Dr Markas Gilmartin, Jon Rolfe, Gareth Rees and Barry Newbury. <br />\n            <br />\n            Through a unique relationship over a number of years , a growing appreciation of two typically distant<br />\n            industries occurred to enable an organic and powerful suite of solutions to evolve. When combined,<br />\n            these services not only strengthen the unique B&amp;B offering but most importantly add real fiscal value<br />\n            to the client. <br />\n            <br />\n            B&amp;B approaches each client with a completely blank piece of paper. We typically evaluate the clients<br />\n            finances as soon as possible to identify any immediate actions to optimise the cash position. We then<br />\n            conduct ''brand and business'' evaluations which include mid and long term ambitions to create a road<br />\n            map for future growth. <br />\n            <br />\n            Brand&amp;Business has shaken up and optimised the traditional service silos by embracing what really<br />\n            matters as an end result – the client''s growth and profitability. </p>\n        ', 11),
(30, 'mojo_region_2', 'Mojo Region 2', 'about', '<p>\n        "As we (the founding partners) learned more about each other''s businesses, we<br /> quickly realised that we wanted the same outcome for our clients; optimisation for<br /> continued client growth. We also identified how we both specialised in the specific<br /> niches of successful UK SME businesses (£1m-£25m turnover).\n        \n        \n        <br /><br />\n        With recessions in full flow and emerging technologies, the world of business is<br /> radically changing. We all need to be faster, sharper and more knowledgeable than<br /> ever before. The great news is that for those that embrace change they can look<br /> forward to 2012 and beyond."  Stuart Dawson, Managing Director\n        </p>\n        ', 11),
(31, 'mojo_region_2', 'Mojo Region 2', 'about', '<p>\n        "As we (the founding partners) learned more about each other''s businesses, we<br /> quickly realised that we wanted the same outcome for our clients; optimisation for<br /> continued client growth. We also identified how we both specialised in the specific<br /> niches of successful UK SME businesses (£1m-£25m turnover).\n        \n        \n        <br /><br />\n        With recessions in full flow and emerging technologies, the world of business is<br /> radically changing. We all need to be faster, sharper and more knowledgeable than<br /> ever before. The great news is that for those that embrace change they can look<br /> forward to 2012 and beyond."  Stuart Dawson, Managing Director\n        </p>\n        ', 11),
(32, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'financial', '<h1>Business optimisation</h1>\n<p> \n\nOur consultants bring decades of experience in optimising the profitability of successful owner-managed businesses. They work closely with CEOs, FDs, MDs and other senior Directors to introduce new methods to minimise liabilities such as corporation and income tax to generate cash back into the business for strategic growth. These options for growth might include expansion, acquisitions, mergers, increasing value for sale or exit.\n</br> \n</br> \nThe initial process is quite simple, it all starts with a brief discussion to learn a little more about your  business and to make sure that you qualify for our optimisation services. Qualification is mostly geared around company size, turnover, profitability and mid / longer term strategies.\n</br> \n </br> \nOnce both parties are comfortable that optimisation can take place, we would then meet to conduct a more detailed review of the business and financial landscape. It is from here that you will learn exactly how much value we can add back into your business.\n </br> \n</br> \n<h1>Individual optimisation</h1>\nB&B also works closely with successful high net worth individuals. This might include TV personalities, celebrities, sports people, comedians and actors. In addition to advanced tax planning and marketing optimisation, there are also a range of other opportunities in areas such as reliefs on income tax, royalties and stamp duty \n</p>\n', 14),
(33, 'mojo_region_2', 'Mojo Region 2', 'financial', ' <p>\n"Our financial consultants are industry leading in their own right, yet when combining the outcomes with the latest principles in marketing and business development, the results can be staggering. More interesting is that we then see the results of increased activity and sales in the subsequent financial year which enables us to optimise profitability even more." Dr Markas Gilmartin, Founding Partner</p>\n         ', 14),
(34, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'marketing', '\n<p class="font_12">\n	Successful SME marketing is very different to start up or big brand activity. An integrated approach must be adopted to ensure that the target market is communicated to effectively and that all activity serves to raise awareness and increase sales.<br />\n	<br />\n	We take time to learn about your business, your customers and your ambitions to create solutions that will enable progress and profitability to take place quicker.&nbsp;In many instances we can multiply our clients marketing resource through advanced financial planning. With more resource comes more options, more activity, more sales and ultimately more profit.<br />\n	<br />\n	Brand&amp;Business is different to many agencies in that we genuinely care about how your business performs and as a result how our marketing services perform. We want to be accountable throughout each process as this feeds back into our financial optimisation, it is this mentality that ensures long-lasting and happy working relationships.<br />\n	<br />\n	&quot;Brand and Business have been an integral extension to our business for the last three years. They&#39;ve taken the time to learn about the mechanics of our company and as a result the brand, marketing and advertising activity continues to go from strength to strength.&quot; Colette Brown MD Prospect Resourcing (UK).<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 12),
(35, 'mojo_region_2', 'Mojo Region 2', 'marketing', ' <p>"It will all start with an exploratory chat. We''ll look forward to learning more about your business and aspirations for the immediate and longer term.  We''ll then work with you to create a roadmap for achieving growth , marketing effectiveness and profitability". Stuart Dawson, Managing Director </p>\n         ', 12),
(36, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'talent', '<h1>Protect your most valuable asset – Your People!</h1>\n          <p class="font_12">Just imagine if your management teams enjoyed a 10% uplift in creativity, efficiency and productivity. The knock-on effects to your business will result in quicker growth and greater profitability not to mention a much happier work force (you included). Our consultants specialise in ground-breaking methods to re-invigorate and retain your talent from board-level to mid-management. <br />\n            <br />\n            Your People are your most important asset. If you lose your talent, the costs to find and train their replacement can be very costly. </p>\n        ', 8),
(37, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'innovate', '<h1></h1>\n<p>\nB&B is a dynamic enterprise that also develops its own, in-house projects through its industry insights, gap analysis, brand marketing and business development practices.\n</br>\n</br>\n\n\nPlease feel free to contact us if you would like to learn more about our in-house projects or how we might be able to partner with each other in the future.\n</br>\n</br>\n\n\n\nHere are just a few of our recent projects and joint ventures in development.\n</p>', 15),
(38, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'news', '\n<div class="cont_L_blog_L">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div class="cont_L_blog_R">\n	<h1>\n		How to win the rugby world cup and save tax</h1>\n	<h2>\n		Friday 3 February 2012</h2>\n	<p class="font_12">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p class="font_12">\n		Improve by 1%</p>\n	<p class="font_12">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		That&rsquo;s the strategy Clive Woodward took when guiding England to the Rugby World Cup.&nbsp;&nbsp;Take 100 parts of the game and improve each by 1%</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		So let&rsquo;s see if we can start to make your business a world beating business.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		Yes, we know tax is dull to a lot of people and is the most overcomplicated, misunderstood area of finance.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We like to make things simple and make your tax work for you .</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		Times are tough at the moment, so squeezing another percentage here or there can mean quite a lot to some people.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		How you do this: very simple, you wait&hellip;.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		If you are near your company year end and eyeing up a big deal, a new client or product sale, why not wait a few more days.&nbsp;&nbsp;HMRC reconfirmed on 6 December that they are reducing the corporation tax rate for large firms for the next 2 tax years by 1 % a year.</p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		Now let&rsquo;s find the other 99 things.</p>\n</div>\n', 13),
