(40, 'mojo_region_1', 'Mojo Region 1', 'contact', '<h1>\n	Its good to talk!</h1>\n<p class="font_12">\n	Whether you are a prospective new client, partner or super talented and interested in joining us, please do get in touch, we&#39;d love to hear from you.<br />\n	<br />\n	Our Covent Garden office is located on the 3rd floor of the prestigeous Hospital Club<br />\n	<br />\n	<a class="link" href="#" title="">http://www.thehospitalclub.com</a><br />\n	<br />\n	The Hospital Club is a unique hub to London&#39;s creative, media and tech industries. Apart from a great place to work, socialise and entertain clients, it has to be one of the best networking environments around.<br />\n	<br />\n	Say hello, we&#39;ll look forward to hearing more about you, your brand and business.</p>\n\n', 16),
